601
00:35:57,420 --> 00:35:58,700
I told you before.


602
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:00,860
The Armoury is a place for men.


603
00:36:01,060 --> 00:36:01,940
You can't go.


604
00:36:02,190 --> 00:36:03,070
Besides,


605
00:36:03,330 --> 00:36:06,140
