606
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,320
All right.


607
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:13,190
You must make sure he finishes it.


608
00:36:13,580 --> 00:36:14,820
When he concentrates,


609
00:36:15,030 --> 00:36:16,340
